CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1945, p. 3, reads: "Westinghouse Grads - These charming young ladies are June graduates of Westinghouse High School.  Left to right, are Zelpha Baltimore, Alma Rector, Alice Robinson, Annamae Mason, Constance Brown, and Alpha Baltimore. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Zelpha Baltimore, Alma Rector, Alice Robinson, Annamae Mason, Constance Brown, and Alpha Baltimore holding bouquets of roses in Harris Studio
